2637 /****************************************************************************
2638 Handling of statement states in functions and triggers.
2639
2640 This is used to ensure that the function/trigger gets a clean state
2641 to work with and does not cause any side effects of the calling statement.
2642

2644 if they are used items that would normally be stored in the binary
